<h2>getopt: C-Like 'getopt' Behavior</h2>
<p>Package designed to be used with Rscript to write
    &ldquo;#!&rdquo; shebang scripts that accept short and long flags/options.
    Many users will prefer using instead the packages optparse or argparse
    which add extra features like automatically generated help option and usage,
    support for default values, positional argument support, etc.</p>
